{"tid":931704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"格陵蘭極速融冰　破350年紀錄","createTime":"2018-12-07T08:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T08:59:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9e9a0b1379642af84645a1b22951e3bb6b3f2c","tid":931704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181207/20563310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F20563310&d=OaCoICW24oY6%2FNaEHQbAyF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=eccf5891\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F20563310&h=ccc5658a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181207/20563310</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月07日 <br />\n<br />\n格陵蘭極速融冰　破350年紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181207/large/a2303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181207%2Flarge%2Fa2303a.gif&h=5015f1da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n格陵蘭融冰速度加快。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n科學家發現格陵蘭的融冰速度破紀錄達新高，過去20年的融冰速度比20世紀平均紀錄高出33%，比工業革命前快50%，使排進大海的冰水增加50%，預計本世紀末水位將再額外上升半米。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：德基民盟今選默克爾繼任人<br />\n<br />\n世紀末水位將再升半米<br />\n<br />\n美國、比利時和荷蘭的科學家前日於科學期刊《自然》發表報告，指由於全球暖化，格陵蘭西部的融冰速度已打破350年來的紀錄，甚至可能是7,000至8,000年來最嚴峻，形容狀況「異常」和「史無前例」，且無減慢迹象。<br />\n<br />\n科學家指，雖然18世紀中期融冰速度開始加快，但至1990年代速度依然平穩和相對較低，2004至2013年是有紀錄以來融冰最持續和密集的10年，2012年錄得可能是7,800年來最大面積的融冰，排水量足夠填滿2.4億個標準泳池。<br />\n<br />\n國際太空總署（NASA）指，格陵蘭是繼南極洲後全球第二大冰面，融冰平均每年使全球水位上升0.8毫米，冠絕全球。格陵蘭冰面厚逾1.6公里，如冰面完全融解可使全球水位上升七米。<br />\n<br />\n有冰川學家指，北極圈氣溫上升，與18世紀中期比較，如今每1℃的暖化會致使雙倍冰量融解，意味水位上升速度加快，人類存亡受威脅，低窪地區和島國更是水浸眼眉。6月另一研究發現南極洲自1992年來融冰量達三萬億噸，過去五年融冰速度增長三倍。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/德新社/《今日美國報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n德基民盟今選默克爾繼任人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n北韓導彈基地新設施曝光<br />\n<br />\n德基民盟今選默克爾繼任人<br />\n疑空中加油訓練出事美兩軍機日本相撞墮海"},{"pid":"44d3c6d19edd1ceec44ab6d336ca7354a1c5cdb4","tid":931704,"uid":82720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"連登唔會有人理"},{"pid":"b984c910453a15a0fb5a94d757af5bbc69c94c16","tid":931704,"uid":151534,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"水浸眼眉都要返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f133aa95d1d52dcd5cce1ebe429bdafbcb31c3f","tid":931704,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d3c6d19edd1ceec44ab6d336ca7354a1c5cdb4","tid":931704,"uid":82720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"連登唔會有人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"梗係有人理啦<br />\n扮假膠講要返工同引戰話人環保撚嗰啲囉<br />\nchild登俾佢地玩到好似Facebook噉"},{"pid":"4faece83e19ac5dce993dec73298aca9811c1c64","tid":931704,"uid":149383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"暖化撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d86a3a097f41f0497f9e2ddbcf5a3a6cb1825f5","tid":931704,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"44d3c6d19edd1ceec44ab6d336ca7354a1c5cdb4","tid":931704,"uid":82720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"連登唔會有人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:50:41.000Z","msg":"個個都戇鳩鳩撐個傻佬侵"},{"pid":"7d98df4d4d2812b7b581e42cea345b4ac77ce301","tid":931704,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"本世紀末2100年"},{"pid":"5be49b3ed040ed60c4b242a07278315bf85308b3","tid":931704,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"暖化撚講兩句?"},{"pid":"b4b37005694129f6a251fa49ed345d700555243d","tid":931704,"uid":5733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"係連登可以講d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登仔表示不了，未知發生緊咩事"},{"pid":"48a8d15674ff34267149e43d8c3e63cc91e031db","tid":931704,"uid":210662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"連登仔最期待既冚球剷來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}